add_amend_rule_motion -  This method adds in a request to amend a rule.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_amend_rule_motion(string area,
int rule_no,
string amendment,
string creator)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^area%^RESET%^ - the area to put the amendment in
%^BOLD%^rule_no%^RESET%^ - the rule to amend
%^BOLD%^amendment%^RESET%^ - the amendment text
%^BOLD%^creator%^RESET%^ - the person doing the amendment
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure
.EI

